Lets make up a list of things verant could do to nerf the uber-monk tank on raids instead of hitting everyone. Dont beat on me, Im not implying we need all that much of a change but if the monk tank is the problem then there are other ways to fix it such as:<br>
<br>
- Put a hard cap on our AC at say 1450 ac. This is a number most warriors can reach and far surpass with equivilant uber equipment but would not put average monks who casually earned there equipment (Who i would imagine sit around 1100-1200 ac at level 60 while giving room to grow with a few really nice items.)<br>
<br>
-Sigh..if they are going to keep the nerf in place then they need to fix the solo abilities for the little guy.  How bout reducing our mend timer abit at high levels? This wouldnt make us better tanks, only better solo people.<br>
<br>
- Sensible solution. Make warriors better tanks instead of nerfing the hell out of us.  Make /shield a permanent ability with a cap of 200-250.  The warriors main purpose is to take damage.  This should be an inate ability on ALL THE TIME not 12 seconds.  <br>
